<section id="faq" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="co">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="an h2 mb-4">Frequently Asked <span class="gr-tx">Questions</span></h2>
      <p class="an d1 text-lg text-gray-600">
        Find answers to common questions about Atom Writer and how it can help your content creation process.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="an d1 space-y-4">
        <div class="faq-item cd overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left font-medium">
            <span>How does the AI writing assistant work?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer overflow-hidden max-h-0 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="p-4 pt-0 text-gray-600">
              Atom Writer's AI assistant analyzes your writing style, tone, and context to provide suggestions that match your unique voice. It uses advanced natural language processing to help with grammar, style improvements, SEO optimization, and can even generate complete content sections based on your input.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item cd overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left font-medium">
            <span>Can Atom Writer create content that sounds like me?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer overflow-hidden max-h-0 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="p-4 pt-0 text-gray-600">
              Yes! Atom Writer learns from your existing content and writing patterns to maintain your authentic voice. The more you use it, the better it becomes at mimicking your style. You can also set specific tone and style preferences, and our AI will adapt to match your unique voice.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item cd overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left font-medium">
            <span>Is there a limit to how many words I can generate?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer overflow-hidden max-h-0 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="p-4 pt-0 text-gray-600">
              Each pricing plan comes with a specific word limit per month. The Basic plan includes 25,000 words, Professional offers 100,000 words, and Enterprise provides unlimited words. If you need more, you can always upgrade your plan or purchase additional words without changing plans.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item cd overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left font-medium">
            <span>How accurate is the content Atom Writer generates?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer overflow-hidden max-h-0 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="p-4 pt-0 text-gray-600">
              Atom Writer's AI produces highly accurate and contextually relevant content. However, as with any AI tool, we recommend reviewing and fact-checking important information, especially for specialized industries. Our AI excels at creating engaging, well-structured content but should be used as a powerful assistant rather than a complete replacement for human oversight.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item cd overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left font-medium">
            <span>Can I use Atom Writer for different types of content?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer overflow-hidden max-h-0 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="p-4 pt-0 text-gray-600">
              Absolutely! Atom Writer supports a wide range of content types including blog posts, social media updates, email newsletters, product descriptions, website copy, ad copy, and more. Each content type has specialized templates and AI configurations to ensure optimal results for that specific format.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item cd overflow-hidden">
          <button class="faq-question w-full flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-left font-medium">
            <span>Is there a free trial available?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer overflow-hidden max-h-0 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="p-4 pt-0 text-gray-600">
              Yes! We offer a 7-day free trial on all our plans with no credit card required. This gives you full access to test all features and see how Atom Writer can transform your content creation process before committing to a subscription.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="an d2 mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Still have questions?</p>
        <a href="#" class="bt bt-pr inline-flex items-center">
          Contact Support
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');
    
    faqItems.forEach(item => {
      const question = item.querySelector('.faq-question');
      const answer = item.querySelector('.faq-answer');
      const icon = question?.querySelector('svg');
      
      question?.addEventListener('click', () => {
        // Close all other answers
        faqItems.forEach(otherItem => {
          if (otherItem !== item) {
            const otherAnswer = otherItem.querySelector('.faq-answer');
            const otherIcon = otherItem.querySelector('.faq-question svg');
            
            otherAnswer?.style.removeProperty('max-height');
            otherIcon?.classList.remove('rotate-180');
          }
        });
        
        // Toggle current answer
        if (answer?.style.maxHeight) {
          answer.style.removeProperty('max-height');
          icon?.classList.remove('rotate-180');
        } else {
          answer.style.maxHeight = answer.scrollHeight + 'px';
          icon?.classList.add('rotate-180');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>